name: Meta-Operant Neurolink Enhancer
description:
Meta-Operant Neurolink Enhancers are a key element of advanced capsuleer neurolink protection technologies.

To further enhance the integrity of capital ship pilot connections, Neurolink Protection Cells are installed with Meta-Operant Neurolink Enhancers used to provide even deeper integration of capsuleer autonomic biosystems with neurolinked ship systems.
